  "short_description": "Pizza Master VR is a fast paced pizza making game. Play in local co-op mode with a waiter, or by yourself in singleplayer. Please customers with drinks and pizzas made from 8 core ingredients. With warm visuals, arcade style gameplay and intuitive controls, who knew pizza making could be so fun?",
